<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٩٦]</span> مُحمَّدُ بنُ خَلفٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سَمِعَ الحَسَنَ، قَوْلَهُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>قالهُ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> حَكَّامٌ، سمِعَ عيسى بنَ يَزيدَ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
